                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The scintillators were all 3.81 cm in",
                "diameter and ranged from 0.159 cm to 0.636 cm in",
                "thickness."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "BCINT",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " First, a low intensity run was made",
                "in which the individual beam particles were counted",
                "with plastic scintillators and C-11 activity was",
                "produced in a thick graphite block. Next, the C-11",
                "activity in a 0.159 cm thick polystyrene target was",
                "determined relative to a digital readout ion chamber",
                "beam monitor in a high-intensity run. Finally, the",
                "C-11 activity in a thick graphite block was also",
                "determined at high beam intensity relative to the ion",
                "chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The C-12(C-12,x)C-11 cross section was",
                "calculated using data from the three runs."
              ]
            }
          ],
